sequenceDiagram
    actor H as Human
    participant CA as /company-add
    participant Pref as ~/.claude/preferences.md
    participant FS as ~/.claude/companies/[name]/

    H->>CA: /company-add [name]

    note over CA: Pre-checks
    CA->>Pref: Check active_company not already set
    CA->>CA: Check for existing knowledge data at global paths
    alt Existing data found
        CA->>H: ⚠️ Data exists — continue? (yes/no)
        H->>CA: yes
    end

    note over CA: Config grilling (one topic at a time)
    CA->>H: Topic 1 — Sprint length + release cadence
    H->>CA: Answers
    CA->>H: Topic 2 — Team locations + timezones
    H->>CA: Answers
    CA->>H: Topic 3 — Change freeze periods
    H->>CA: Answers
    CA->>H: Topic 4 — Compliance tier + frameworks
    H->>CA: Answers
    CA->>H: Topic 5 — External approval gate (CAB/RFC)
    H->>CA: Answers
    CA->>H: Topic 6 — Deployment environment chain
    H->>CA: Answers
    CA->>H: Topic 7 — AI usage policy
    H->>CA: Answers
    CA->>H: Topic 8 — Tools policy (prohibited/required/approved)
    H->>CA: Answers

    CA->>H: Present full config summary. Proceed? (yes/no)
    H->>CA: yes

    note over CA: Scaffold
    CA->>FS: Create directory structure
    CA->>FS: Write config.md (fully populated)
    CA->>FS: Write tools.md (skeleton entries from Topic 8)
    CA->>FS: Write registry.md + projects/registry.md
    CA->>FS: Write knowledge/ stub files (Raw/ Wiki/ Outputs/)
    CA->>FS: Write rules/README.md
    CA->>FS: Write setup.sh + .claude/CLAUDE.md
    CA->>FS: Bundle 17 company knowledge skills
    CA->>Pref: Set active_company: [name]

    CA->>H: ✅ Setup complete — next steps (fill config, /knowledge-onboard, /add-system, /company-git)

    note over H,FS: Optional follow-up
    H->>CA: /company-git [remote-url]
    CA->>FS: git init + add remote
    H->>CA: /company-sync
    CA->>FS: Pull then push knowledge base with team
